<br>
That's about the only difficulty, though.  Beasties get access to some wicked fierce hand to hand weapons, their epic is extremely nice (similar to a ranger epic, but BLs can't double attack so they get lesser damage for the same ratio), they have a huge range of very nice spells (chloro, alacrity, mini-focus, talisman, etc).  Spiritual Purity and Savagery are also nice spells.<br>
<br>
A beastlord is like any other class on a raid, you just gotta find your niche and do your job.<br>
